.TH "drm_fb_helper_lastclose" 9 "drm_fb_helper_lastclose" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_fb_helper_lastclose \- DRM driver lastclose helper for fbdev emulation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" drm_fb_helper_lastclose
.BI "(struct drm_device *dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
DRM device
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function can be used as the \fIdrm_driver->lastclose\fP callback for drivers
that only need to call \fBdrm_fb_helper_restore_fbdev_mode_unlocked\fP.
